            "sanskrit": ["kārpaṇya-doṣopahata-svabhāvaḥ", "pṛcchāmi tvāṁ dharma-sammūḍha-cetāḥ", "yac chreyaḥ syān niścitaṁ brūhi tan me", "śiṣyas te ’haṁ śādhi māṁ tvāṁ prapannam"],
