            "sanskrit": ["na hi prapaśyāmi mamāpanudyād", "yac chokam ucchoṣaṇam indriyāṇām", "avāpya bhūmāv asapatnam ṛddhaṁ", "rājyaṁ surāṇām api cādhipatyam"],
