                "2": "āhaveṣu mitho ’nyonyaṁjighāṁsanto mahī-kṣitaḥyuddhamānāḥ paraṁ śaktyāsvargaṁ yānty aparāṅ-mukhāḥ",
                "3": "yajñeṣu paśavo brahmanhanyante satataṁ dvijaiḥsaṁskṛtāḥ kila mantraiś cate ’pi svargam avāpnuvan",
