            "sanskrit": ["arjuna uvāca", "paraṁ brahma paraṁ dhāma", "pavitraṁ paramaṁ bhavān", "puruṣaṁ śāśvataṁ divyam", "ādi-devam ajaṁ vibhum", "āhus tvām ṛṣayaḥ sarve", "devarṣir nāradas tathā", "asito devalo vyāsaḥ", "svayaṁ caiva bravīṣi me"],
