            "sanskrit": ["na veda-yajñādhyayanair na dānair", "na ca kriyābhir na tapobhir ugraiḥ", "evaṁ-rūpaḥ śakya ahaṁ nṛ-loke", "draṣṭuṁ tvad anyena kuru-pravīra"],
